# Project 2

## Importing the data
```{r}
data = read.csv('oil.csv')
head(data)
```
```{r}
str(data)
```
```{r}
data <- data %>% setNames(c('Date', 'Price'))
data$Date <- as.Date(data$Date)
```

## Plot before imputing
```{r}
ggplot(data, aes(x = Date, y = Price)) +
  geom_line() +
  labs(title = "Oil Prices Over Time",
       x = "Date",
       y = "Oil Price") +
  theme_minimal()
```
